name: Figura 55
description:
“Figury” (eng. Figures) is a series of generative artworks combining curves and grids into more complicated shapes, that create rich,  suprising compositions. Each figure is also a drawing, plotted with AxiDraw A3 pen plotter.

Purchase of this piece comes with getting a physical drawing. Upon resale on the secondary market the physical drawing shall be sent to the new owner. Shipping will be covered by the new owner.

Creation date: 17.06.2021

Plotted with:
Rotring Isograph 0.2mm on A3 bristol board

Digital version: PNG, 3506x4959px

Made by Jakub Antolak with React, Typescript, and Node.js
